                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Complex Select with nested resultmaps:
                        <a href="http://code.google.com/p/mybatis/source/browse/sub-projects/scala/trunk/mybatis-scala-samples/src/main/scala/org/mybatis/scala/samples/resultmap/SelectWithResultMapSample.scala">Code</a>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Complex Select with nested selects
                        <a href="http://code.google.com/p/mybatis/source/browse/sub-projects/scala/trunk/mybatis-scala-samples/src/main/scala/org/mybatis/scala/samples/nestedselect/NestedSelectSample.scala">Code</a>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Insert:
                        <a href="http://code.google.com/p/mybatis/source/browse/sub-projects/scala/trunk/mybatis-scala-samples/src/main/scala/org/mybatis/scala/samples/insert/InsertSample.scala">Code</a>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Update:
                        <a href="http://code.google.com/p/mybatis/source/browse/sub-projects/scala/trunk/mybatis-scala-samples/src/main/scala/org/mybatis/scala/samples/update/UpdateSample.scala">Code</a>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Delete:
                        <a href="http://code.google.com/p/mybatis/source/browse/sub-projects/scala/trunk/mybatis-scala-samples/src/main/scala/org/mybatis/scala/samples/delete/DeleteSample.scala">Code</a>
